AN ACT
To repeal sections 43.656, 56.265, 67.2540, 168.071,
190.142, 210.1080, 210.1505, 211.326, 324.012,
324.035, 329.050, 337.618, 339.100, 455.050, 542.301,
566.010, 566.147, 566.148, 566.149, 566.150, 566.151,
566.155, 566.211, 566.218, 567.030, 573.010, 573.023,
573.025, 573.035, 573.037, 573.038, 573.050, 573.052,
573.110, 573.112, 573.215, 589.015, 589.042, 589.400,
589.414, 590.050, 595.045, 610.131, 650.120, and
660.520, RSMo, and to enact in lieu thereof fifty-two
new sections relating to sexual offenses, with
penalty provisions.
Be it enacted by the General Assembly of the State of Missouri, as follows:
