67 trafficking training, consistent with the guidelines
68 established in section 210.1505, before such submission;
15

69 (iii) Any licensee who submits an application for
70 relicensure after December 31, 2028, and before January 1,
71 2030, shall have completed three hours of sex and human
72 trafficking training, consistent with the guidelines
